OL,3,CWho are Hezbollah and why is the group
OL,4,Cinvolved in fighting with Israel?
OL,6,FIn a joint statement, the 12-strong
OL,7,Fbloc calls for the temporary pause in
OL,8,Ffighting "to provide space for
OL,9,Fdiplomacy towards the conclusion of a
OL,10,Fdiplomatic settlement", as well as a
OL,11,Fceasefire in Gaza.
OL,13,FThe calls for calm come after Israel
OL,14,Fand Hezbollah have spent days trading
OL,15,Fwaves of strikes, killing hundreds of
OL,16,Fpeople and forcing tens of thousands
OL,17,Fin Lebanon to flee their homes.
OL,19,FIsrael and Hezbollah have been
OL,20,Fexchanging fire across the border
OL,21,Fsince the October 7 attack by Hamas.
